<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    h1, h2, h3 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .team-name {
      color: #2980b9;
    }
    .match {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        box-shadow: none;
        padding: 10px;
      }
      body {
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      h1, h2, h3 {
        font-size: 1.25em;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Hey  <%= user.name %>! 🎉</h1>
    <p>Congratulations, you've joined the ranks of the <strong> <%= league.name %></strong> warriors! 🔥 Brace yourself for an action-packed season that's sure to keep you on the edge of your seat. 🎮</p>

    <h2>League Details</h2>
    <p>🌟 League:  <%= league.name %><br>

    <h2>Mark your calendars! 📅</h2>
    <p>🚀 Blast-off Date: <%= new Date(round1Date).toLocaleDateString() %><br>
    🏁 Finish Line: <%= new Date(lastDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>

    <h2>🏆 Meet Your Fellow Gladiators:</h2>
    <ul>
        <% for (const team of teams) { %>
            <li class="team-name">🛡️ <%= team.name %></li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>

    <h2>🥊 Match Schedule of Destiny:</h2>
    <% for (const round of roundMatches) { %>
        <h3>⚔️ Round <%= round[0].round %>:</h3>
        <% for (const match of round) { %>
            <% const homeTeam = teams.find(team => team.id === match.home_team); %>
            <% const awayTeam = teams.find(team => team.id === match.away_team); %>
            <p class="match">📅 <%= new Date(match.date).toLocaleDateString() %> <%= homeTeam.name %> 🆚 <%= awayTeam.name %></p>
        <% } %>
    <% } %>

    <p>Ready, set, go! 🚦 Dive into the exhilarating world of <%= league.name %> and show off your skills. 🌟</p>

    <p>If you need a helping hand or have questions, our legendary support team is just a message away. 💌</p>

    <p>Best of luck, champion! 🏆</p>
    <p>Your friends at,<br>
    🚀 Customer Support Team</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>